# resultType

**Instance Property**

The type of result that this request returns.

## Declaration

```swift
var resultType: NSPersistentHistoryResultType { get set }
```

## Discussion

This value defaults to [doc://com.apple.coredata/documentation/CoreData/NSPersistentHistoryResultType/transactionsAndChanges].

## Configuring the Request

- **fetchRequest**: The specified fetch request, when retrieving history.
